media-chromecast-slideshow-large-directories - Check Large Media Directories

USAGE:
    media-chromecast-slideshow-large-directories <media-directory>

DESCRIPTION:
    Check media directories for large file counts that may cause
    performance issues with Chromecast slideshow.

ARGUMENTS:
    media-directory
        Root media directory to check (required)

CONFIGURATION:
    -conf-media-share-max-files-per-directory NUM
        Maximum files per directory threshold (default: 100)
        more than 100 causes chromecast to choke

EXAMPLES:
    media-chromecast-slideshow-large-directories /media/photos
    media-chromecast-slideshow-large-directories ~/Pictures
